      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty. It's honestly in showroom condition\u2014I've babied this car from day one and it still looks and feels brand new. Not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Come take it for a spin, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
