    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S. This wide-body specimen features the naturally aspirated 3.6L horizontally opposed six-cylinder powerplant, delivering linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is superlative; the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with an LN Engineering ceramic upgrade, and the rear main seal remains bone dry. Chassis dynamics are exceptionally sharp, utilizing the factory-spec all-wheel-drive system and ventilated cross-drilled rotors clamped by four-piston monoblock calipers. Finished in flawless Arctic Silver over a supple black leather interior, the vehicle exhibits zero parasitic draw or fluid seepage. A true driver's car with impeccable service provenance and zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
