    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the original floor mats are spotless, and it still retains that fresh factory scent. Every electronic component, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained exclusively at the dealership with a comprehensive folder of service records included. With exceptionally low mileage and a clean title, this vehicle is indistinguishable from new and ready for a collector or a driver who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
